00:00:29.450 --> 00:00:31.140
Two Youngest

00:00:31.140 --> 00:00:37.579
Victor De Leon III AKA "Lil Poison" is the
world's youngest signed professional gamer.

00:00:37.579 --> 00:00:41.989
In 2005 at the age of 7 he signed a deal with
Major League Gaming and set the record. He

00:00:41.989 --> 00:00:47.699
started with the dreamcast at the age of two
playing NBA 2K and entered his first competition

00:00:47.699 --> 00:00:51.059
in New York at the age of four, a Halo tournament.

00:00:51.059 --> 00:00:56.350
Julian is the world's youngest professional
drummer as of March 21st 2012 when he was

00:00:56.350 --> 00:01:02.210
5 years 10 months and 3 days old. He began
drumming on his father's lap at just 3 months.

00:01:02.210 --> 00:01:06.920
At 15 months he was offered a contract to
be a member of the Cleveland cavaliers drumline

00:01:06.920 --> 00:01:10.130
and at 20 months he recorded his first album.

00:01:10.130 --> 00:01:11.630
Three oldest:

00:01:11.630 --> 00:01:17.219
86 year old Johanna Quaas holds the record
for oldest gymnast. She performed a parallel

00:01:17.219 --> 00:01:22.659
bar and floor demonstration at the 2012 Cottbus
Challenger Cup in Germany. She didn't even

00:01:22.659 --> 00:01:28.240
take up gymnastics until she was 30 but now
regularly participates in senior gymnastics

00:01:28.240 --> 00:01:31.109
competitions where she has won multiple awards.

00:01:31.109 --> 00:01:37.680
The worlds oldest surviving photograph was
taken by Joseph Nicephore Niepce in 1826,

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:42.539
called "View from the Window at Le Gras".
The photo was lost for 50 years after being

00:01:42.539 --> 00:01:48.600
exhibited in London and rediscovered by Helmut
Gernsheim in 1952 and is now typically on

00:01:48.600 --> 00:01:50.640
display in Austin, Texas.

00:01:50.640 --> 00:01:57.640
The oldest convicted bank robber was 92 when
he robbed a bank in Texas in 2003. J.L Hunter

00:01:58.079 --> 00:02:03.079
Rountree, nicknamed "Red" pleaded guilty to
stealing $1,999 and was sentenced to 151 months.

00:02:03.079 --> 00:02:06.609
It was his third and last robbery, his first
took place in 1998 at the age of 86. He claimed

00:02:06.609 --> 00:02:10.890
that he was trying to get back at the banks
for the financial ruin they had put him in.

00:02:10.890 --> 00:02:14.349
A documentary called "This Is Not A Robbery"
is based on his story.

00:02:14.349 --> 00:02:16.349
Four Most Expensive:

00:02:16.349 --> 00:02:21.849
Chris Evans a UK radio and television personality
has the record for buying the most expensive

00:02:21.849 --> 00:02:28.849
car. He paid $17.7 million (12 million pounds)
for a 1963 Ferrari 250 GTO, one of only 36

00:02:30.799 --> 00:02:37.769
ever made. It has a top speed of 174 MPH and
goes 0 to 60 in 6.1 seconds.

00:02:37.769 --> 00:02:43.760
A bottle of 1947 Cheval-Blanc Bordeaux wine
set the record for most expensive wine sold

00:02:43.760 --> 00:02:50.760
at auction for $304,375 on November 16th 2010
that crushed the expected price tag of $150,000

00:02:53.500 --> 00:02:55.010
to $200,000.

00:02:55.010 --> 00:03:00.060
In May of 2012 the record was set for Worlds
most expensive hot dog at Capitol Dawg in

00:03:00.060 --> 00:03:07.060
Sacramento, Cal for $145.49. It's called the
California City Capitol Dawg and includes

00:03:08.269 --> 00:03:14.069
Swedish Moose cheese that has to be flown
in and goes for $200 a pound. Since then there

00:03:14.069 --> 00:03:18.069
have been some more expensive hot dogs that
technically don't hold the record yet. At

00:03:18.069 --> 00:03:25.069
New Yorks 230 Fifth they created a $2300 hot
dog that includes 60 day dry aged Wagyu beef

00:03:26.189 --> 00:03:32.189
topped with onions caramelized in Dom Perignon
and 100 year old balsamic vinegar, sauerkraut

00:03:32.189 --> 00:03:37.120
braised in Champagne and mixed with caviar
and topped with Gold.

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:42.680
The Red Tibetan mastiff holds the record for
the most expensive dog ever sold. The 11 month

00:03:42.680 --> 00:03:49.680
old puppy named Big Splash or "Hong Dong"
in Chinese sold for 10 million yuan or $1.5

00:03:49.780 --> 00:03:55.969
million in China by a breeder in 2011. Hong
Dong weighs in at 180 pounds and is three

00:03:55.969 --> 00:04:01.329
feet tall. In related news the newest record
holder for tallest dog is a great dane named

00:04:01.329 --> 00:04:05.650
Zeus from Michigan that is 7 foot 4 on his
hind legs!

